\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces  Forward predictions of binary mixture effects on the time to reach metamorphosis (Gosner stage 42). \textit  {Fraction of tadpoles} is the number of test organisms which have not yet reached metamorphosis, relative to the total number of surviving individuals.   Rows correspond to 2,4-D exposure concentrations, columns to Flupyradifurone exposures (both in $mg/L$). Variability in model output reflects individual variability. Error bands indicate 5th to 95th percentiles. }}{17}{figure.caption.10}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:mixture_fracttadpoles}{{6}{17}{Forward predictions of binary mixture effects on the time to reach metamorphosis (Gosner stage 42). \textit {Fraction of tadpoles} is the number of test organisms which have not yet reached metamorphosis, relative to the total number of surviving individuals. \\ Rows correspond to 2,4-D exposure concentrations, columns to Flupyradifurone exposures (both in $mg/L$). Variability in model output reflects individual variability. Error bands indicate 5th to 95th percentiles}{figure.caption.10}{}}
